Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:17.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}胸口憋得好闷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}内心情绪高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:31.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我本来寻找命运之恋
